title: The Merri Table at CERES
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. CERES sits on a 13 acre plot of land. Offers market stall and shop as well a cafe. All food and drinks are organic, local, and seasonal - from breakfast and lunch dishes to pastries and sandwiches to cakes and sweets.
